data.description: Nice 3 bedroom, 1 bahroom home in a great location! Living room and dining room combo with hardwood floors, large front window and closet. Large eat in kitchen with tile floor, wood cabinetry, gas stove, 2 windows and a door to a nice rear yard! Follow straight hardwood steps to the second floor, which hosts three bedrooms with windows and closets as well as a newer full bath with all tile floor, tile tub area and jacuzzi-type tub. Basement is super clean and partially finished- great for a den, sitting area, office or playroom and also features a rear storage room.
